{"tid":2175241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"官不排除警員捏造供詞指不能盡信 港大生脫襲警罪 惟堵路罪成明判刑","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T13:14:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed34590e5dcbcef8e2f6d3d4df65feb67d74032a","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/E6E2K3HS4JEDTJHOSJCGYATXXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FE6E2K3HS4JEDTJHOSJCGYATXXI%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=bf67f57e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FE6E2K3HS4JEDTJHOSJCGYATXXI%2F&h=04b887f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/E6E2K3HS4JEDTJHOSJCGYATXXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年11.11發起「黎明行動」三罷及堵路，20歲港大護理系男生被指於大埔公路堵路及襲警，案件早前審理。裁判官陳炳宙今裁決時指，<strong><span class=\"red\">警員作供有可能誇大修飾，不排除捏造，且自相矛盾，證供質素欠佳，不能盡信，裁定襲警罪脫</span></strong>，惟另一項在公眾地方造成阻礙的傳票則罪成，案件押至明天判刑。"},{"pid":"05d1d78a82c3716b04043d52def2797153a2a115","tid":2175241,"uid":227271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"某裁判官：證明警員無夾口供"},{"pid":"c96f9bb4590217c2a447ed317e6a1a3cbb770e28","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"主審裁判官陳炳宙在裁決時指，當時休班警員沈德華駕駛私家車行經現場，看見兩名身穿黑衣的人將防撞桿拋出路面，沈接載報稱遇襲的Y重返現場，Y及沈兩人先後下車追截黑衣人。<br />\n<br />\n陳官指沈要在觀察的五秒內既要注意行車安全，又要識別黑衣人的衣著、外貌，甚至可說出眼鏡框顏色。陳官認為沈的供詞令人難以置信，有證供誇大修飾的可能。<br />\n<br />\n此外，沈同意身為便衣休班警，對疑犯行使武力時表露警察身份一事重要。然而，沈在警方書面供詞稱在制服被告後表露身份，但在庭上卻供稱已立即表露身份。陳官不排除沈捏造有關說法，沒有道出全部事實，不接納沈的證供。<br />\n<br />\n至於報稱被襲的遇襲警員Y，陳官認為Y的證供自相矛盾，起初稱下車目的是拘捕，其後改口稱為「初步調查」，但行車紀錄儀顯示Y下車前已知悉要拘捕堵路疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n此外，Y是在將被告柙解回警署，見到值日官後才跟沈說出被襲一事。陳官質疑Y報稱被襲，為何不在現場告訴沈？由沈以襲警罪被告？Y更沒有通知值日官，而陳官亦認為Y描述有關被告的襲警動作不自然。總而言之，陳官認為Y證供質素欠佳，不可盡信，基於控方未能舉證至毫無合理疑點，裁定被告襲警罪脫。"},{"pid":"cce950842715197500f69f5a505302304910ce3c","tid":2175241,"uid":122915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"其實我對於法官對證人證供既評價方面唔可以當做一個好似RESUME咁樣既留底紀錄黎去判斷返整個機關往後既可信程度真係好撚ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619db2ef62250abdf62280306f23ff80fd29a9d9","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d1d78a82c3716b04043d52def2797153a2a115","tid":2175241,"uid":227271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"某裁判官：證明警員無夾口供"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:08:42.000Z","msg":"呢單都係粉嶺法院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd155e1023de7f4b86fead15cb34ff433efcb3c","tid":2175241,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c414c4853f3a1a8832a464b151114720bc4b55","tid":2175241,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"另外個條大唔大機會要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6ac7634fa0287c6005ea94a629b55385b3d623","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"陳官在裁決前指，發現聆訊證據與傳票內容出現差異，例如「三個防撞欄」應為「三支防撞桿」，以及被阻道路應由「一條行車線」改為「兩條行車線」，終決定根據《裁判官條例》第27條修改傳票內容。<br />\n<br />\n陳官並批評指，控方早於開審前曾修改傳票內容，聆訊期間亦沒再修改傳票內容，表現強差人意。<strong><span class=\"red\">陳官直言，如果控方及警員留意證據，應不難發現當中差異；惟他強調法庭並非懲罰疏忽職守的機構，故今除修改傳票內容，亦批准辯方就改傳票內容一事取得訟費。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7709377392e6f63b02613c641a205b149ecacfa5","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57c414c4853f3a1a8832a464b151114720bc4b55","tid":2175241,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"另外個條大唔大機會要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"近期幾單判80-120小時社會服務令"},{"pid":"a316edb126c32d54293b24e8986ca2fc8a16896e","tid":2175241,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲官愈來愈少了"},{"pid":"1c08e37a0c887e20c5e0f7ccbb0fdec527bd080e","tid":2175241,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7709377392e6f63b02613c641a205b149ecacfa5","tid":2175241,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57c414c4853f3a1a8832a464b151114720bc4b55","tid":2175241,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"另外個條大唔大機會要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"近期幾單判80-120小時社會服務令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"咁都定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 做完好走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e20d69d10b19360a55ffb47c99e3a114911852","tid":2175241,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db5c8da7749885257a10328355f1a53616c7b79","tid":2175241,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"Deadbody wins again"},{"pid":"e1d1c2552eb5ddc11ca92d4285785fd5e65869e1","tid":2175241,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e824679686a677f083621ec1c7bcb498a8adff3","tid":2175241,"uid